metadata.name: GUY NORCAL x RAZVANGART - SUMMER I Derivative
metadata.description:
A special collaboration with a special "GUY"

Placed Guy's typographic work SUMMER I over one of my works from THE TREE OF POWER project.

Summer always has been one of my most dearest seasons and it was a strong reason why I chosed SUMMER I to serve as layer over a piece from my most special projects. Really enjoyed doing this!

Guy's entire collection can be found here:
https://opensea.io/collection/seasonsoflife1
